elephone within 5 working days of receipt of the invoice amount to the Seller’s bank account, providing the opportunity to make a new order or refund the amount paid by the Buyer.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">6. When using CarClinic e-shop, the Buyer undertakes to take into account that photos of goods shown are illustrative and may slightly differ from the actual appearance of goods, To obtain more accurate and complete information about the product. the Buyer can contact the Seller via CarClinic e-shop, at e-mail address: info@Carclinic.com.bd, or by telephone: 01334565657<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">7. When using CarClinic e-shop, the Buyer is required to: a. Ensure that all information provided by him/her when using CarClinic e-shop is correct. b. Not to transmit unlawful or otherwise prohibited information. c. Not to use CarClinic e-shop for speculative or inaccurate acts or fraud.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 30px -25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Jost, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--tp-text-secondary); line-height: 26px; transition: 0.3s ease-out; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">ORDERING AND CONCLUDING CONTRACT OF SALE &amp; PURCHASE:</b><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1. To complete the order for a selected item in Carclinic e-shop, the Buyer must add the item to the virtual shopping cart by clicking the \"\"Add to cart\"\" button. In a case the Buyer wishes to 